<item>
            <title>[FLINK-1724] TestingCluster uses local communication with multiple task managers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1724</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Starting a task manager via TestingUtils does not respect the number of configured task managers and mis-configures the task managers to use local network communication (LocalConnectionManager instead of NettyConnectionManager).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12782825">FLINK-1724</key>
            <summary>TestingCluster uses local communication with multiple task managers</summary>
